<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Order Confirmation</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f4f4f4;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
        }

        .container {
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            background-color: #ffffff;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #dddddd;
        }

        .header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            color: #333333;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 20px;
        }

        .content h4 {
            margin-top: 0;
        }

        .order-details {
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .order-details th, .order-details td {
            padding: 10px;
            border: 1px solid #dddddd;
            text-align: left;
        }

        .order-details th {
            background-color: #f8f8f8;
        }

        .order-summary {
            margin-top: 20px;
            width: 100%;
            border-collapse: collapse;
        }

        .order-summary th, .order-summary td {
            padding: 10px;
            text-align: right;
        }

        .order-summary th {
            text-align: left;
        }

        .footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dddddd;
            font-size: 12px;
            color: #777777;
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>Your IT Training BD's Order is Confirmed</h1>
            <p>And we're just as excited as you are.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h4>Here's what you ordered:</h4>
            <table class="order-details">
                <tr>
                    <th>Order #</th>
                    <th>Order Date</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= order._id %></td>
                    <td><%= order.date %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table class="order-details">
                <tr>
                    <th>Item</th>
                    <th>Qty</th>
                    <th>Cost</th>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <td><%= order.name %></td>
                    <td>1</td>
                    <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
            <table class="order-summary">
                <tr>
                    <th>Subtotal:</th>
                    <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
                <tr>
                    <th>Total:</th>
                    <td>$<%= order.price %></td>
                </tr>
            </table>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>&copy; 2024 IT Training BD. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>
